snippet.title: Chiki Chiki Machine Mou Race | Wacky Races - Live! 3DO Magazine Trailer
snippet.description:
As seen on the first issue of Live! 3DO Magazine from Japan, this is a preview of Chiki Chiki Machine Mou Race, based on the Hanna-Barbera cartoon Wacky Races.

Developed and published by Future Pirates
Wacky Races (C) Warner Bros. Discovery
Also on PC
